transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Haan sir, India Mart se Abdul bol raha hu sir.
Customer: Haan Abdul bhai boliye.
Executive: Sir aapke paas mera number hai na to aap us pe call kyun nahi karte sir ki aap customer care pe call karte hain?
Customer: Customer care pe phone karne jaruri hai sunai nahi dete bhaiyya.
Executive: Kya?
Customer: Are us pe phone karne se sunai nahi sakte aap.
Executive: Us pe phone karne se?
Customer: Un un us pe phone karne se sunte nahi khudte khudte.
Executive: Sir us pe phone karoge to bhi main call karunga mujh pe call karenge to bhi main karunga maine ye Saddam sir ko bhi bola tha Saddam sir keh rahe the aapke bare mein unko samjha dene ke liye phone nahi karne ke liye us pe.
Executive: Ab bar bar aap us pe call karenge to hum aapko to wahi solution denge na sir.
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Ab bataiye sir kis liye aapne call kiya tha main main itna call kar raha hu na to Saddam sir phone uthate hain na aap uthate hain sir.
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Ji.
Executive: Haan kis liye call kiya tha sir bataiye aap.
Customer: Apne paas mein ye ground ye business nahi aa rahi hai.
Executive: Kya sir?
Customer: Ground net.
Customer: Hello.
Customer: Ek minute thodi der baad me baat karta hu.
Executive: Main keh raha hu kis liye call kiya tha batayenge sir to main solution provide karaunga sir aapko kya issue tha?
Customer: Ground net ground net.
Executive: Ground net ki inquiry nahi aa rahi hai.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Ek minute ruk jaiye.
Executive: Bolo.
Executive: Itna sir aap ab ye hai na ki koi response bhi nahi karta na aap hum log jab call karte hain to aap log response bhi nahi karte problem ye bhi hai.
Customer: Ab aap ye product kar paoge.
Executive: Sir main keh raha hu koi solve tick karega tabhi to hum log kuch kaam karenge ab aapne customer care pe phone kar diya hum phone karte hain koi uthata hi nahi hai phone response bhi nahi karte to jab aap log response nahi karenge to service kaise provide karaenge aap bataiye sir.
Customer: Line pe.
Customer: Sir main thodi der baad me phone pe karta hu aapko na.
Executive: Ab yahi hai main check kar raha hu to sir aap kahenge thodi der ki baat yahi hai na aap thoda line pe rahiye main ek bar check kar leta hu kya hai sir main aapko inquiry provide karata hu batata hu sir kaun si by lead use karna hai.
Executive: Ab aapne call kiya to main uska solution de raha hu sir ji.
Executive: Thoda line pe rahiye.
Executive: Line pe rahiye sir main ek minute.
Customer: Sir ye na sir ye na.
Executive: Aapne bataya hai ground net.
Customer: Ye dekho.
Executive: Sir inquiry to aayi hai isme bhi dekhiye kafi sari by lead available hai.
Customer: Haan aayi hai.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan aayi hai. Sir aaj ke liye sir aaj ke date mein inquiry aayi hai aapke paas ye dekhiye by lead available hai ground net bhi hai oil cake.
Customer: Kitne tan ki?
Executive: Sir ek tan ki hai sir.
Customer: Kitne tan ki aapko chahiye bataiye. phone de sakta hu aapko 10 minute mein abhi abhi 15 tan ki inquiry aayi hai sir.
Customer: Are 10 minute mein phone. Sir aap suniye to main aapko bata raha hu 15 tan ki bhi inquiry aayi hai sir yaha pe 430000.

- Executive explained the buyleads process.

- Executive confirmed groundnut buyleads are available.

- Executive provided details of available buyleads.
